long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
It is frustrating when you try to use the ChatGPT but are simply denied access. That should always work, right? 😓

And that's exactly what's happening now, once you've installed this extension in your browser, you'll never see the "chatgpt is low on capacity" message again! That's right - now you can enjoy the workflow without worrying about getting problems with your connection. 🏃💨

And the best part? Our extension is completely free! 🫶
